    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Front-end developer, multimedia producer, photographer, passionate about food and cooking, and the city of São Paulo, I have worked in the front-end development area since 2011. During that year, I noticed a great connection between design, user experience and development, and I believe these are all great components in making a project successful.</p>
    <p>Currently, I am trying to contribute to the development community by helping in Open Source projects, like <a href="//locaweb.github.io/locawebstyle" title="Locaweb Style" class="aj-link-locawebstyle">Locaweb Style</a>.</p>

