    <h4>Where I've been</h4>

    <h5><a href="//d3.do/en/" class="aj-link-d3">d3</a><em>june/15 - Present</em></h5>
    <p>D3 help driven people to deliver innovation using software, hardware and design.</p>
    <p>Now ... I'm here.</p>

    <h5><a href="//thegoodfellas.com.br/" class="aj-link-goodfellas">The Goodfellas</a><em>April/15 - May/15</em></h5>
    <p>the goodfellas is a creative and technology digital company focused on designing and producing interactive experiences in advertising.</p>
    <p>I was Front-end freelancer to work in two projects, <a href="//gatorade.com.br" class="aj-link-border">Gatorade Brazil</a> and the <a href="//shitproject.com" class="aj-link-border">Shitproject</a>, inside these projects, I learned a lot about animation rules and used animation tools like <a href="//greensock.com/tweenlite" class="aj-link-border">TweenLite</a> to the development.</p>

    <h5><a href="//locaweb.com.br" title="Locaweb" class="aj-link-locaweb">Locaweb</a> <em>September/13 - January/15</em></h5>
    <p>Here I worked in the Front-end team to the Locaweb products, and with the help of UX and Design team, we have developed an open source <a href="//locaweb.github.io/locawebstyle" title="Locaweb Style" class="aj-link-locawebstyle">framework</a> to meet all the basic needs of products Locaweb. Take a look and tell me what you think.</p>
    <p>At Locaweb, I helped develop the <a href="//www.locaweb.com.br/produtos/smtp-locaweb.html" title="SMTP Panel" class="aj-link-smtp">SMTP Panel</a> (<a href="http://locaweb.github.io/locawebstyle/documentacao/exemplos/painel2/pre-painel/" title="See example in Locaweb Style documentation" class="aj-link-smtp">see example</a>), a Platform for sending e-mails and automated notifications that also uses the Locaweb Style.</p>
    <p>I also contribute in projects like:</p>

